	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissime ac colendissime pater, deus te servet nobis incolumem atque salvum diutissime votaque tua omnia fortunet!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non ita pridem scripsi ad te fusissime et ad reliquos praeceptores meos omni officio observandos, misi praeterea tres meos discipulos <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basilaeam</placeName> etiam <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20351" cert="low">Mischcovios</persName>, quorum unus est germanus frater eorum, qui cum <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3988">Wolphio</persName> vivunt, duo reliqui patrueles illorum, nostri palatini <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l260" cert="high">Cracoviensis</placeName> nepotes.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Intermittere tamen nolui etiam in mediis meis gravissimis occupationibus, quin ad has proximas nundinas <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l157" cert="high">Francoford[iam]</placeName> aliquid ad te scriberem et eandem cantilenam canerem<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><bibl>Adagia</bibl>, 2, 5, 76 (<bibl>LB</bibl> II 574).</note> de perturbatissimo videlicet rerum omnium cum religionis tum public..</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">civilique in nostra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Sarmatia</placeName> statu.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam ut de confusione <placeName type="auto_name">Arianicae</placeName> et anabaptisticae religionis taceam, cuius progressum cum <persName type="auto_name">Blandraticis</persName> oraculis ad vos misimus, scito, huic regno a tribus potentissimis hostibus magna pericula impendere.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Moschus</persName> copiosissimis exercitibus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l841" cert="high">Lituaniam</placeName> invasurus est, nisi deus avertat.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name">Tartari</placeName> superioribus diebus in finibus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2561">Podoliae</placeName> multa depopulando ac vastando damna dederunt, omnes autem propter <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turcam</placeName> numerosissimo exercitu descendentem in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l882" cert="high">Hungariam</placeName> timent, ne vicinum bellum, quamvis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turca</placeName> cum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polono</placeName> foedere unctus sit, irruptionibus et incursionibus in regni fines valde noxium sit ac perniciosum.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">A <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2562">Prussia</placeName> quoque nescio quid novi affertur, quasi et ibi cogitarent de defectione, proinde amplissima legatio est eo missa.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8100">Scalichius</persName> male hic audit, vix effugiet principum manus.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1936">Lismanini</persName> horrenda morte ex meis literis, quas...</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nos oramus filium dei regnantem ad patris dexteram, ut ipse ecclesiam et gloriam suam adversus furores diabolorum his postremis mundi temporibus tueatur vosque et ecclesiam vestram in tranquili statu florere patietur.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cui me et officia mea humiliter commendo atque saluto universos tuamque imprimis domesticam ecclesiam.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iterum vale, pater omni observantia colendissime.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Datum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l260" cert="high">Cracoviae</placeName> calendis augusti 1566.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Addictissimus ac tui observantissimus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8511" cert="high">Christophorus Thretius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo atque piissimo viro do... mini d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henricho Bul[lingero</persName>, ex]imio Iesu Christi servo, [Tigurinae ecc]lesiae pastori fidelissimo, [domino et] patri omni observantia colendo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
